99
00:07:30,853 --> 00:07:32,283
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak apa.</font>

100
00:07:32,483 --> 00:07:33,953
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan yang sejujurnya.</font>

101
00:07:35,353 --> 00:07:37,953
