145
00:10:27,953 --> 00:10:29,323
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka tampaknya dekat.</font>

146
00:10:31,223 --> 00:10:32,293
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak mungkin.</font>

147
00:10:33,483 --> 00:10:34,653
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau cemburu?</font>

148
00:10:35,653 --> 00:10:37,553
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya ampun, itu omong kosong.</font>

149
00:10:38,323 --> 00:10:40,483
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika Eun Bong Hee itu waras,</font>

150
